the true king of the south ! lil wayne has truly developed and grown over the years and this cd is only a taste of what 's to come.lil wayne is one of the best rappers in the industry right now.he 's the best rapper out the south ( behind mac ) ! he has a unique flow and some really diverse lyricism.tha carter 2 is a instant classic and it was the best release of 2005 in the hip-hop/rap category ! lil wayne is on top of his game , as he released 5 solo albums,3 group albums , most recently a duo album with baby and has a numerous amount of mixtapes.if you have n't cop this cd yet , then you are truly missing out on a great classic ! keep bringing that fiya music weezy f baby